Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KAEDE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, you should get up soon.\NBreakfast will be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede-san's symptoms could be those\Nof a type of dissociative disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dissociative disorder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An illness where there is a loss of sense\Nand awareness that you are yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As is the case with Kaede-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,patients experience symptoms\Nincluding omission or memory loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, she has no memories of living\Nwith her parents or big brother to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's believed that extreme stress or\Nmental trauma can cause this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede developed Puberty Syndrome due to\Npeople badmouthing her on social media, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It caused Kaede to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}DIE, KAEDE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So much that she decided to sever a part\Nof her memory to escape that crushing feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She did so to protect from\Nbeing totally broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why it's dissociative...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Kaede lost her memory,\NI didn't know how to interact with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I was hesitant...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, I brought you a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking forward to\Nthe new volume of this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... So "Kaede-san" really liked these books?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way she talks is different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How she holds chopsticks is different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The order she eats her dishes is different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She buttons her pajamas from the top.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way she walks is different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's different from Kaede...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Different... Different...\NEverything about her is different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Kaede has...\NShe has bruises all over her body again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Kaede...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom wasn't able to accept\Nwhat happened to Kaede.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's fine, you'll be fine, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she ended up with mental illness herself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as for me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the hospital I was brought to,\Nnobody would believe my story.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how much I explained, they thought\Nit was a preconception, something mental,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that the wounds were self-inflicted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't do anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't do anything for Kaede.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was sick of everything,\Nand snuck out of hospital one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was when I met her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The distance to the horizon seen at eye level\Nis roughly four kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko-san quietly listened to my story,\Nand believed every bit of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From then on, I snuck out of the hospital\Ntime and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko-san was always there\Nat Shichirigahama Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you thinking about\Nyour little sister again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about you, Shoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You were having lewd thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why you\Nbelieved what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About Kaede's wounds, my scar,\Nand Puberty Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I said,\Nnobody would listen to me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody believes what I've seen\Nwith my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are as many worlds to see\Nas there are people in them, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like how the horizon you can see\Nis further than the horizon I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same for the ocean breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some will say it feels refreshing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,while others say they dislike it because\Nit makes their skin and hair feel sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was some sort of fate\Nthat brought us together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so as a senpai in life,\NI'll give you some wonderful advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do people normally say "wonderful"\Nfor their own stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have a big dream or\Nhigh hopes for my life, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I was still able to\Nfind meaning for my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What I think, Sakuta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is that life is here for us to become kinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To become kinder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I live life every day hoping that I'm a\Nslightly kinder person than I was the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what, Shoko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to live my life like you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you know of pain\Nthat others cannot understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can become kinder\Nthan anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure you can be supportive\Nof someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These values were unknown to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KAEDE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was released from the hospital,\NI bought a pen and notebook on the way home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said yesterday how\Nyou should write some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened that day,\Nwhat you thought. It can be anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should start with your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I can write it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Kaede" is spelled like "Flower,"\Nfollowed with "Maple" like the tree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should write "Kaede" in all hiragana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiragana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The person here right now\Nis the current "Kaede."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for everything 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's only you, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who understands Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KAEDE AZUSAGAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trusting you with Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you take care of Mom, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.\NYou don't have to over do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and I will be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede is afraid of how everyone looks at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is looking at "Kaede-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, I wanted Kaede's\Nmemories to return, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted her to come back to us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, if that came to be,\Nwhat would happen to the current Kaede?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the whole story about Kaede.\NSorry I kept quiet about it until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NYou were looking out for Kaede, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, as I watched Kaede\Nslowly becoming friends with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bring myself to mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it was okay to stay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I'm not that mad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you told us a bit earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you ARE mad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}NOVEMBER 17th
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good morning, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede might not make it much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her whole body is in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You frolicked around a lot yesterday,\Nso you just have muscle cramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A film shoot in Kanazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I won't be able\Nto see you for a while again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're filming at a studio in Tokyo\Nuntil the day after tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll be coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Call me if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you even if nothing happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I meant if something happens\Nto Kaede-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, I'm home—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be a good girl and stay asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since making it all the way\Nto the beach yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede doesn't want this good groove\Nto be interrupted by muscle cramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede wants to head outside again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Seriously?\N- Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's your uniform debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a uniform debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. The outside world\Nisn't going anywhere, so no need to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kaede all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, Kaede doesn't know the girl we met\Nat the beach yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's someone "Kaede-san" knows, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to know,\NI'll tell you what kind of a girl she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede has trouble dealing\Nwith people who know "Kaede-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's troubling, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not knowing is scary, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was Kotomi Kano,\Nan acquaintance from before kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She used to live above us\Nin the same apartment complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She used to play with "Kaede"\Nfrom a very young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she was at the beach\Nthinking about rereading this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Poison Apple the Prince Gave Me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she borrowed it from "Kaede."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be friends with Kae-chan again\N—Kotomi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,friends
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Komi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede! Just now—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede! Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, until Kaede-san is conscious again,\NI can't say anything for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, there's a possibility that there will be\Na change to her memories when she awakens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAEDE AZUSAGAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kaede isn't the type\Nyou'd call a princess, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You collapsed and brough here\Nin an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did Big Brother change Kaede's clothes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't, so relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was done by the nurse and Mai-san,\Nwith some help from Toyohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been fine if you did it, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're Kaede... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede is still Kaede, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaede has regained consciousness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Test results showed no abnormalities,\Nso she may be released today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fact she collapsed may indicate\Nthat "Kaede's" memories are coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaede regains her previous memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's a possibility that all of her\Ncurrent memories will disappear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}TAXI AREA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was Dad here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaede, what do you want\Nto do the most right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eat pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something to celebrate your hospital release.\NIt can be something bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eat a giant pudding, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can eat that, but I was talking more\Nabout going to see pandas or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pandas are second on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's first?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOVEMBER 19th
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kaede says that she wants to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to grant her that wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain the situation to her middle school\Nbefore tomorrow ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you know, it's all right to do it\Nafter everything settles down, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should introduce me to\Nthe girl you're dating right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah, when things settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOVEMBER 20th
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The shoot in Kanazawa\Nwas going to be for two weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I'm sure you'll be lonely not seeing me,\Nbut I'll be sure to call you every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait in front of the phone every night!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take life more seriously and study.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So Sakuta, you're not scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about Kaede-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm scared.\NI'm about to wet my pants as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking a serious question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But as a big brother, there are things\Nyou never show a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Piss, poop... and whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm the big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there was something I could do,\NI'd like to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez, I'm such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister didn't say anything about it\Nbecause there was nothing we could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOVEMBER 22nd
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello, I'm Tomobe, the school counselor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At first, it can be as simple as\Nwalking to school for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't have to start in the classroom.\NYou can go to the nurse's office first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would the nurse's office count\Nas going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's different from everyone else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But even though they may look the same,\Neveryone is actually different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, there are tall kids and short kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some kids are good at running,\Nand some are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Each person has their own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if it's the result\Nof you doing your best,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's fine to say that it counts\Nas you "going to school."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, it can be circled\Neven if it's the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Circled?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Circling this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,* GO TO SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, Kaede would definitely like\Nto go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you think she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like they're laughing\Nabout you, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can make people laugh\Nthat easily, you're sorely mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-The path of the comedian is a steep one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We tried hard today, so why don't we\Nhead back and eat some pudding?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede is determined to finally make it\Nall the way to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She will do her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so impatient about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaede is not being impatient!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even Tomobe-san said\Nyou can take it slow, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:16:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, let's take a break\Nfrom practicing today, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to overdo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is a need to overdo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede doesn't have the time to take it slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, she knew about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?\NTotally cracking me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Too wicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they no good!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede wants to go to school!\NWhy won't they move at all!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede will not go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not home...\Nbut practice until she can go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it so that\Nyou can go to school, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll resume practice\Nafter a short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A break?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in the best place I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're scared of this many people,\Nyou'll never make it to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay. Will try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big Brother, are we at this "best place" yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There. We have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Zoo! It's the zoo, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it was the best place\NI could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like Nasuno before a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It does smell like beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Pandas! Big Brother, there's the pandas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are pandas right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pandas! Pandas are walking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That panda over there is eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pandas are big.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd expect "giant" pandas to be big.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it looked over at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The panda is eating again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They said on TV before that\Nbamboo isn't very nutritious,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so pandas need to spend a majority\Nof the day eating to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tough life being a panda, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is doing their best\Nto live their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, it's the lesser pandas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are lesser.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're "lesser," after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede really loves pandas after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit lonely to say goodbye to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can just come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Kaede is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is for you. An annual pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you can come see pandas\Nevery day if you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing!\NBig brother really is a big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for Kaede to come back here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the effort of buying it,\Nso it'd be a waste of money not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede wants to come here many times\Nand get our money's worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede was able to make a purchase, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to carry that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede purchased the pudding,\Nso Kaede will carry it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, our house is that way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A shortcut, didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're still an amateur\Nwhen it comes to roads around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a seasoned veteran?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could call me a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-The school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's night now, so stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You shouldn't, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're only going to peek in for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a little bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your first trip to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is class 3-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Kaede's classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time at school\Nwill hopefully be in the daytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've conquered school at night,\Nthat should be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, every goal\Nin the notebook can be circled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's been that many already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Panda, pudding and school\Nwere the last to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but school will still be a triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd be okay circling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be for after\Ncoming to school during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there is a feeling\Nthat it can be accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:23:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede feels like she can head to school\Nduring the day tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.06,0:23:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looking forward to tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.23,0:23:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really can't wait for tomorrow to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOVEMBER 27th
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That is you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, my legs are so swollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did run around the zoo a lot yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't go.\NBig Brother, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, was my room always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.\NSheesh, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.80,0:24:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from you, Big Brother.\NSuch a rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.01,0:25:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Time\N#13 The Dawn After an Endless Night
